"/es/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Crea un nuevo <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\" title=\"DOM/DocumentFragment\">DocumentFragment</a></code>&nbsp;vacio, dentro del cual un nodo del DOM puede ser adicionado para construir un nuevo arbol DOM fuera de pantalla.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var fragment = document.createDocumentFragment();\n</pre>\n\n<p>Se crea un objeto<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\" title=\"DOM/DocumentFragment\">&nbsp;DocumentFragment</a>&nbsp;vacio, el cual queda listo para que pueda insertarseles nodos en el.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas_de_uso","title":"Notas de uso","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\" title=\"DOM/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a>&nbsp;son Nodos&nbsp;del DOM&nbsp;que nunca forman parte del arbol DOM. El caso de uso mas comun es crear un&nbsp;<em>document fragment</em>, agregar elementos al <em>document fragment</em> y luego agregar dicho <em>document fragment</em> al arbol del DOM. En el arbol del DOM, el <em>document fragment</em> es remplazado por todos sus hijos.</p>\n\n<p>Dado que el <em>document fragment </em>es generado en memoria y no como parte del arbol del DOM, agregar&nbsp;elementos al mismo&nbsp;no causan&nbsp;<a href=\"https://code.google.com/speed/articles/reflow.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">reflow</a> (computo de la posicion y geometria de los elementos) en la pagina. Como consecuencia,&nbsp;usar&nbsp;<em>document fragments</em> usualmente resultan en&nbsp;<a href=\"http://ejohn.org/blog/dom-documentfragments/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">mejor&nbsp;performance</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Tambien puede utilizarse el constructor <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>documentFragment</code></a> para crear un nuevo fragmento:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">let fragment = new DocumentFragment();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este ejemplo crea una lista de los principales navegadores web en un <em>DocumentFragment</em>, y luego adiciona el nuevo subarbol DOM al document para ser mostrado.</p>\n\n<p>HTML</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;ul id=\"ul\"&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;</pre>\n\n<p>JavaScript</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var element  = document.getElementById('ul'); // assuming ul exists\nvar fragment = document.createDocumentFragment();\nvar browsers = ['Firefox', 'Chrome', 'Opera',\n    'Safari', 'Internet Explorer'];\n\nbrowsers.forEach(function(browser) {\n    var li = document.createElement('li');\n    li.textContent = browser;\n    fragment.appendChild(li);\n});\n\nelement.appendChild(fragment);</pre>\n\n<p>Resultado</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"600\" height=\"140\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/es/docs/Web/API/Document/createDocumentFragment/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad de navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_de_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.Document.createDocumentFragment","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Document/createDocumentFragment/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificaciónes","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>DOM Level 2: <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-35CB04B5\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">createDocumentFragment</a></li>\n <li>DOM Level 3: <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Core/core.html#ID-35CB04B5\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">createDocumentFragment</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Vea También","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation/createDocument\"><code>document.implementation.createDocument()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>documentFragment</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Notas de uso","id":"notas_de_uso"},{"text":"Ejemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Compatibilidad de navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_de_navegadores"},{"text":"Especificaciónes","id":"specification"},{"text":"Vea También","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Crea un nuevo DocumentFragment vacio, dentro del cual un nodo del DOM puede ser adicionado para construir un nuevo arbol DOM fuera de pantalla.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.createDocumentFragment()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Document.createDocumentFragment()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"document.createDocumentFragment","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.createDocumentFragment()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document.createDocumentFragment()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"document.createDocumentFragment","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Document.createDocumentFragment()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Document.createDocumentFragment()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document.createDocumentFragment()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/document/createdocumentfragment","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/document/createdocumentfragment/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Document/createDocumentFragment","title":"Document.createDocumentFragment()"}],"pageTitle":"Document.createDocumentFragment() - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}